      </b-tab>

<script>
import BCardCode from '@core/components/b-card-code'
import { BTabs, BTab, BCardText } from 'bootstrap-vue'
import { codeFill } from './code'

export default {
  components: {
    BCardCode,
    BTabs,
    BTab,
    BCardText,
  },
  data() {
    return {
      codeFill,
    }
  },
}
</script>
